  {% call components.section("Style") -%}
    <p>There are a variety of elements that can be used in a form depending on the kind of information that needs to be collected from users.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/form/form-style.svg' | url }}" alt="Form specs" style="--inline-img-max-width: 640px;">
    </div>
